    <header>
        <h1>Electric Bill Consuming Discussion</h1>
    </header>
    <section>
        <h2>Understanding Electricity Consumption</h2>
        <p>Electricity consumption plays a crucial role in determining the amount of your LESCO bill. The more appliances you use, the higher the consumption, leading to increased costs.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Factors Affecting Your LESCO Bill</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Usage of High-Power Appliances:</strong> Devices like air conditioners, heaters, and refrigerators consume more electricity.</li>
            <li><strong>Peak Hour Usage:</strong> Electricity rates are often higher during peak hours, affecting your monthly bill.</li>
            <li><strong>Energy Efficiency:</strong> Using energy-efficient appliances and LED lights can help reduce your bill.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>How to Reduce Your Electricity Bill?</h2>
        <p>To lower your LESCO bill, consider the following tips:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Unplug unused electronic devices to prevent phantom energy loss.</li>
            <li>Use solar panels to reduce dependence on grid electricity.</li>
            <li>Opt for energy-efficient appliances and smart meters.</li>
        </ol>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Useful Resources</h2>
        <p>For more details on LESCO billing and energy-saving tips, visit <a href="https://lescobillcheckonline.com.pk/" target="_blank">LESCO Official Website</a>.</p>
    </section>
